    "description": "<p><strong>Join Our Team at Green Avenue Home for the Elderly</strong></p>\n<p>Are you ready to make a difference in the lives of the elderly? At Green Avenue Home for the Elderly, we've been doing just that since 2009. Our 76-bed facility, nestled in a charming old-world building, caters to both private and subsidized residents, creating a diverse and enriching environment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why Choose Us:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Legacy of Care:</strong> With over a decade of experience, we've been dedicated to providing excellent quality care to the elderly sick.</p>\n<p><strong>Holistic Approach: </strong>We're committed to promoting active living for our residents, ensuring their physical, emotional, and social well-being.</p>\n<p><strong>Passionate Professionals:</strong> Our team is passionate about our role as professional caregivers and trainers, imparting care with strong moral values.</p>\n<p><strong>Heartfelt Care:</strong> At Green Avenue, we care with our head, heart, and hands, going above and beyond to make a meaningful impact.</p>\n<p>Join us in creating a compassionate and thriving community. Your skills and dedication will contribute to a brighter future for our residents.&nbsp;</p>",
